instructions: Plate the plate on the Charger
Place the Napkin on the Plate on the Charger
Place the Dinner Fork beside the charger facing upwards
Get the Salad fork place upwards beside the Dinner Fork
Get the Dinner Knife and place on the right side of the charger
Place the Tea spoon beside the Dinner Knife
Get the soup spoon and place beside the Tea spoon
Get a water Glass and place in front of the Charger
Get a Wine Glass and place beside the Water Glass
Add another wine Glass, beside the first wine Glass
Get a coffe cup and place beside the wine Glass close to the Soup Spoon
Get a bread plate and place in front of the Dinner and the Salad Forks
Plate a butter knife on the Bread plate
Place a desert Fork in between the water Glass and Bread plate
Add a desert spoon beside the desert fork close to the Charger
